actor User
boundary EditProductPage
control ProductController
participant ":ProductService" as ProductService
participant ":ProductModel" as ProductModel
database Database

User->EditProductPage: 1. Open product edit form
activate EditProductPage
activate User

User->EditProductPage: 2. Edit product fields and submit
EditProductPage->EditProductPage: 3. Validate form input
activate EditProductPage
space
deactivate EditProductPage

opt Check validation
    EditProductPage-->User: 3.1. Show validation error
end

EditProductPage->ProductController: 4. PUT /products/{id}
activate ProductController

ProductController->ProductService: 7. Process product update
activate ProductService

alt Product not found
    ProductService->ProductModel: 8.1. Find product by ID
    activate ProductModel

    ProductModel->Database: 8.1.1. Retrieve product data by ID
    activate Database
    Database-->ProductModel: 8.1.2. Result (null)
    deactivate Database

    ProductModel-->ProductService: 8.1.3. Return not found
    deactivate ProductModel

    ProductService-->ProductController: 8.1.4. Return not found result
    ProductController-->EditProductPage: 8.1.5. Return 404 Not Found + message
    EditProductPage-->User: 8.1.6. Show error: "Product not found"
else Product exists
    ProductService->ProductModel: 8.2. Update product fields
    activate ProductModel

    ProductModel->Database: 8.2.1. Persist updated product data
    activate Database
    Database-->ProductModel: 8.2.2. Update success
    deactivate Database

    ProductModel-->ProductService: 8.2.3. Return updated entity
    deactivate ProductModel

    ProductService-->ProductController: 8.2.4. Return UpdateProductResponse
    deactivate ProductService
    ProductController-->EditProductPage: 8.2.5. Return 200 OK + updated product data
    deactivate ProductController
    EditProductPage-->User: 8.2.6. Show success message
end

deactivate EditProductPage
deactivate User
